  "title": "clear searchbox button doesn't work !",
  "body": "I have two instantsearch like this and  create one search box to search both of of them together.\r\n\r\n```\r\nvar searchProduct = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: '...',\r\n  apiKey: '...', \r\n  indexName: 'market_products'\r\n});\r\n\r\nvar searchShop = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: '...',\r\n  apiKey: '...',\r\n  indexName: 'market_shops'\r\n});\r\n\r\nvar searchBox = instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\r\n  container: '#searchBox2',\r\n  placeholder: 'جستجو'\r\n});\r\n\r\nsearchProduct.addWidget(searchBox);\r\nsearchShop.addWidget(searchBox);\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nwhen I want to clear search box the button works for **product** but it doesn't clear value for **shop**.\r\nit seems that shop query doesn't work. what should I do ?\r\n",
